Description: A toolkit for estimating and bounding persuasion effects in
    instrumental variable settings with binary outcomes. You provide the
    outcome, the treatment, and the instrument, and 'persuasio' computes
    average and/or local persuasion rates. Based on Jun and Lee (2023)
    <doi:10.1086/724114>.
